title: Deva
subTitle: A police officer investigates the murder of his close friend. However, he suffers a traumatic accident that wipes away his memory, jeopardising the investigation.

title: Pal Pal Dil Ke Paas
subTitle: Saher plans to expose Karan, who runs a trekking company, but ends up falling in love with him. However, tension arises when Saher's former lover decides to win her back.

title: Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara
subTitle: Friends Kabir, Imran and Arjun take a vacation in Spain before Kabir's marriage. The trip turns into an opportunity to mend fences, heal wounds, fall in love with life and combat their worst fears.

title: Boonie Bears: Back to Earth
subTitle: When Bramble merges with an alien artefact, he gains incredible abilities. With Avi by his side, he embarks on a high-stakes journey to defend their home from an intergalactic danger.

title: Kesari
subTitle: A Sikh havildar and his soldiers put their lives on the line to protect Saragarhi from the Afghans. The battle goes down in history as a shining example of their valour.

title: No Entry
subTitle: A gorgeous club dancer's ill-timed rendezvous opens up a Pandora's box of lies, absurdities and misunderstandings in the lives of three quirky couples.

title: Dream Girl
subTitle: A man lands a call center job by mimicking a woman's voice, gaining fame and a loyal fan base. However, his double life spirals out of control when rabid clients overstep boundaries.

title: Ab Tumhare Hawale Watan Saathiyo
subTitle: Kunal falls in love with Shweta and decides to stay in the army to get close to her but soon finds out that she is waiting for her husband Rajeev to return from war.

title: Chori Chori Chupke Chupke
subTitle: Raj and Priya, a married couple, hire Madhubala, a prostitute, as the surrogate mother of their child. Trouble brews when Madhubala falls in love with Raj and insists on keeping the child.

title: Kalki 2898 AD
subTitle: In a post-apocalyptic world, a group of people set out to save a woman pregnant with Lord Vishnu's 10th and final avatar, Kalki, from an evil supreme god-king, Yaskin.

title: Kalki 2898 AD

title: Go Goa Gone
subTitle: Things take a dangerous turn when the aftermath of a rave party causes three friends to get stranded on an isolated island infested with zombies.

title: Lakshya
subTitle: Karan, an aimless young man, joins the Indian Army on a whim but backs out when he finds a soldier's life to be difficult. When this creates conflict with his girlfriend, he rejoins to make her proud.

title: State of Siege: Temple Attack
subTitle: Armed with state-of-the-art equipment and a brilliant plan, National Security Guard commandos risk their lives to save innocent people caught in a terrorist attack on a temple in Gujarat.

title: Double Dhamaal
subTitle: Four idlers make elaborate plans to earn money by investing in buildings but are conned by Kabir, who leaves them unemployed and penniless. Soon, they are on the prowl to avenge their humiliation.

title: Saaho
subTitle: An undercover agent and his partner go after a thief who has stolen 2,000 crore rupees. Soon, they realise that the case is linked to the death of a crime lord and an emerging gang war.

title: Koi ... Mil Gaya
subTitle: A young man with special needs is influenced by his father's scientific work. He encounters an alien who grants him extraordinary abilities and transforms his life.

title: Chakra Ka Rakshak
subTitle: A police officer and soldier team up and decide to end the cybercriminals that pose a threat to the safety of people on the Internet.

title: Vivah
subTitle: Poonam, a traditional young woman, gets engaged to Prem, a wealthy man. Their faith and love are tested when an accident occurs and leaves Poonam with first degree burns.

title: Dabangg 3
subTitle: Chulbul Pandey, a corrupt police officer, leads a happy life with his wife and family. However, when his past enemy returns to wreak havoc, he must protect his loved ones from harm.

title: Dabangg 3
subTitle: Chulbul Pandey, a corrupt police officer, leads a happy life with his wife and family. However, when his past enemy returns to wreak havoc, he must protect his loved ones from harm.

title: Mission Majnu
subTitle: An undercover Indian spy takes on a deadly mission to expose a covert nuclear weapons program in the heart of Pakistan that could destroy the free world.

title: Luck by Chance
subTitle: Vikram can't believe his luck when he is chosen for a Bollywood lead role. However, the role may ruin his relationship with his girlfriend.

title: Ground Zero
subTitle: Following the brutal attack on Parliament in 2001, armed police officer Dubey takes the lead in an investigation against Ghazi Baba.

title: Apaharan
subTitle: Ajay, an aspiring policeman, borrows money from a moneylender to pursue his dream. However, he is unable to repay the loan on time and decides to be a part of a kidnapping scheme.

title: God Tussi Great Ho
subTitle: When an anchor, Arun, who is down on his luck, blames God for his misfortunes, God decides to give him his powers for ten days. Soon chaos ensues when Arun decides to grant everyone's wishes.

title: Sanam Teri Kasam
subTitle: A librarian, cast out by her family, asks her neighbour to help her find a suitable husband. However, their growing feelings for each other complicate the situation.

title: Sky Force
subTitle: Brave heroes embark on a quest for truth as India and Pakistan enter an airstrike war that threatens to pose deadly consequences.

title: Karan Arjun
subTitle: Karan and Arjun, two brothers driven by revenge, are murdered by their uncle while seeking justice for their father's death. However, they resurrect years later to settle their unfinished score.

title: Bimbisara
subTitle: Getting betrayed by his brother, ancient evil king Bimbisara teleports to the modern-day world and traps in the mirror. Desperate to return to his empire, Bimbisara searches for the mirror to break free.
